.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lance%20Bass%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20two%203-year-old%20kids%20also%20think%20it's%20fun%20to%20watch%20me%20change%20my%20CGM%20sensor%2C%20used%20to%20measure%20glucose%20levels%20providing%20real%20time%20readings%2C%20and%20like%20to%20see%20my%20glucose%20levels%20on%20my%20phone.%20I%20try%20to%20explain%20my%20diabetes%20to%20them%20in%20a%20kid-friendly%20way.%20Even%20though%20they%20might%20not%20fully%20understand%20it%20yet%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20important%20to%20be%20open%20about%20it%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFun%20fact%3A%20I've%20also%20learned%20that%20people%20with%20diabetes%20can%20still%20consume%20sugar.%20However%2C%20they%20need%20to%20manage%20it%20carefully.%20Sure%2C%20I%20can%20have%20the%20birthday%20cake%2C%20but%20just%20a%20few%20bites.%20It's%20about%20balance%2C%20checking%20my%20glucose%20levels%2C%20monitoring%20the%20way%20I%20eat%2C%20and%20portion%20control.%20And%20now%20I%20can%20get%20away%20with%20housing%20Reese's%20Peanut%20Butter%20Cups%20on%20my%20nightstand%20in%20case%20my%20glucose%20levels%20drop%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f1344ed-b219-4437-a87a-cdc0ab83e130%5C%22%3EI've%20figured%20out%20my%20new%20lifestyle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20lucky%20to%20have%20diabetes%20during%20a%20time%20when%20it's%20much%20easier%20to%20manage%20than%20it%20was%20five%20years%20ago.%20The%20first%20time%20a%20CGM%20sent%20information%20to%20a%20cellphone%20was%20in%202015%2C%20and%20since%20then%2C%20they've%20gotten%20more%20accurate%20and%20discreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lance%20Bass%20with%20husband%20Michael%20Turchin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68387737ca50259add4d4925%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELance%20Bass%20says%20he's%20the%20healthiest%20he's%20ever%20been.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lance%20Bass%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20diagnosis%2C%20I%20was%20constantly%20pricking%20my%20finger%20to%20measure%20my%20blood%20sugar.%20It%20was%20incredibly%20time-consuming%20and%20challenging%20to%20keep%20up%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20use%20a%20Dexcom%20G7%20continuous%20glucose%20monitor%20(CGM)%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20am%20now%20an%20ambassador%20for%20%E2%80%94%20that%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20manage%20my%20diabetes.%20This%20small%20wearable%20measures%20my%20blood%20glucose%20and%20helps%20me%20identify%20factors%20that%20maintain%20my%20glucose%20levels%2C%20such%20as%20incorporating%20electrolytes%20and%20weightlifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20doctors%2C%20I've%20figured%20out%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fhow-to-treat-diabetes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elifestyle%20adjustments%3C%2Fa%3E%20work%20best%20for%20me.%20I'm%20increasingly%20wary%20of%20the%20health%20information%20I%20see%20on%20social%20media%2C%20especially%20if%20it%20isn't%20coming%20from%20a%20licensed%20professional.%20Now%20that%20I'm%20blocking%20out%20the%20noise%2C%20I'm%20the%20healthiest%20I've%20ever%20been%20and%20feel%20confident%20managing%20my%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20calling%202025%20my%20%26quot%3Byear%20of%20yes%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20to%20me%20means%20taking%20every%20opportunity%20to%20travel%20and%20experience%20everything%20I%20can.%20This%20is%20a%20180%20from%20how%20I%20felt%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20my%20diabetes%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flance-bass-diabetes-diagnosis-death-sentence-healthy-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748690282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6838ba346ffb6822ec61c108%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flance-bass-diabetes-diagnosis-death-sentence-healthy-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20type%201.5%20diabetes%20diagnosis%20in%202021%2C%20Lance%20Bass%20found%20a%20new%20path%20to%20health%2C%20balance%2C%20and%20saying%20yes%20to%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lance%20Bass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flance-bass-diabetes-diagnosis-death-sentence-healthy-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20clever%20way%20that%20Domino's%20is%20making%20AI%20feel%20more%20real%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20better%20at%20taking%20your%20pizza%20order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221936%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20holds%20a%20pizza%20box%20in%20a%20navy%20heat-saving%20bag.%20The%20pizza%20box%20says%20%26quot%3BDomino's%20Pizza%26quot%3B%20on%20it%20in%20white%20letters%20on%20a%20blue%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6290f62214f00200181011d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Domino's%20pizza%20being%20delivered%3Cp%3EGabrielle%20Bienasz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvoice-ai-vc-startups-tech-innovation-2025-1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVoice%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20already%20part%20of%20restaurants'%20drive-thru%20and%20phone%20ordering%20systems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20some%20companies%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20their%20AI%20assistants%20sound%20more%20like%20real%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDomino's%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20uses%20different%20accents%20for%20its%20AI%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-ai-create-new-jobs-not-kill-entry-level-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20finding%20its%20voice%20%E2%80%94%20and%20using%20it%20to%20take%20your%20weeknight%20pizza%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERestaurants%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdominos-customers-carrying-out-pizzas-recession-fears-not-deliveries-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDomino's%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Wingstop%2C%20have%20used%20voice%20AI%20assistants%20for%20years%20to%20chat%20with%20customers%20on%20the%20phone%20and%20take%20their%20orders.%20Lately%2C%20though%2C%20they've%20been%20finessing%20those%20assistants%20by%20adding%20region-specific%20accents%2C%20adjusting%20their%20tone%2C%20and%20making%20other%20changes%20that%20make%20them%20more%20natural%20for%20customers%20to%20converse%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20hears%20a%20really%20off-putting%2C%20unrelatable%20voice%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20hang%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lily%20Clifford%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20Rime%20Labs%2C%20which%20developed%20the%20text-to-voice%20model%20that%20Domino's%20and%20Wingstop%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20restaurant%20chains%20are%20using%20voice%20AI%20to%20take%20customers'%20orders.%20But%20Rime's%20experience%20shows%20that%20it's%20not%20as%20easy%20as%20shoving%20an%20AI%20assistant%20with%20a%20robotic%20voice%20in%20a%20drive-thru%20or%20on%20one%20end%20of%20a%20phone%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERime%20develops%20the%20text-to-voice%20technology%20that%20Domino's%20uses%20for%20phone%20ordering.%20Another%20company%2C%20ConverseNow%2C%20provides%20the%20AI%20assistant%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20ConverseNow%20started%20working%20with%20Domino's%20about%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20used%20a%20different%20voice%20that%20many%20customers%20didn't%20want%20to%20speak%20with%2C%20said%20Akshay%20Kayastha%2C%20director%20of%20engineering%20at%20ConverseNow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20one%20point%20where%2050%25%20of%20the%20people%20were%20just%20saying%20they%20just%20didn't%20want%20to%20talk%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20a%20human%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERime's%20technology%20has%20pushed%20that%20number%20closer%20to%20100%25%2C%20Clifford%20said.%20Domino's%20uses%20the%20text-to-voice%20feature%20in%20about%2080%25%20of%20its%20phone%20orders%20in%20North%20America%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20should%20sound%20like%20someone%20who%20could%20work%20at%20Domino's%20and%20not%20someone%20who%20is%20a%2020th-century%20American%20broadcast%20radio%20announcer%2C%26quot%3B%20Clifford%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20develop%20its%20technology%2C%20Rime%20built%20a%20recording%20studio%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20recorded%20a%20variety%20of%20people%20having%20conversations%20with%20a%20friend%20or%20a%20family%20member.%20The%20goal%2C%20Clifford%20said%2C%20was%20to%20capture%20what%20day-to-day%20speech%20sounds%20like%20instead%20of%20using%20voice%20actors%20reading%20rehearsed%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resulting%20technology%20can%20use%20a%20variety%20of%20speech%20patterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDomino's%20customers%20who%20order%20by%20phone%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20reach%20an%20AI%20assistant%20that%20speaks%20with%20a%20Southern%20accent.%20Rime%20says%20that%20it%20has%20also%20developed%20a%20voice%20that%20speaks%20using%20African-American%20Vernacular%20English.%20The%20voices%20that%20Rime%20uses%20don't%20belong%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscarlett-johansson-openai-voice-dispute-may-regret-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereal%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%2C%20Clifford%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETone%20is%20another%20area%20where%20Rime's%20technology%20has%20improved%20voice%20AI%2C%20Kayastha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20restaurant%20chain%20that%20ConverseNow%20works%20with%20pointed%20out%20a%20problem%20with%20an%20earlier%20version%20of%20the%20startup's%20voice%20AI%3A%20It%20sounded%20more%20chipper%20than%20most%20fast-food%20workers.%20Rime's%20technology%20helped%20match%20the%20tone%20to%20the%20situation%2C%20Kayastha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20in%20real%20life%20speaks%20so%20cheerfully%20at%20a%20drive-thru%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20turn%20it%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20voice-to-text%20technology%20also%20correctly%20pronounces%20specific%20menu%20items%2C%20such%20as%20MeatZZa%2C%20a%20Domino's%20pizza%20with%20pepperoni%2C%20ham%2C%20Italian%20sausage%2C%20and%20beef.%20That's%20key%20for%20restaurants%2C%20Clifford%20said%2C%20given%20all%20of%20the%20unconventional%20spellings%20and%20limited-time%20offers%20that%20appear%20on%20their%20menus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDomino's%20has%20grown%20its%20online%20ordering%20options%20lately.%20Customers%20can%20place%20orders%20on%20Domino's%20website%2C%20through%20its%20app%2C%20or%20through%20third-party%20services%20like%20Uber%20and%20DoorDash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20phone%20orders%20remain%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20pizza%20chain's%20business%2C%20CEO%20Russell%20Weiner%20said%20during%20an%20earnings%20call%20in%20late%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20large%20number%20of%20our%20customers%20coming%20in%20on%20online%20ordering%2C%20but%20we%20still%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20phones%20are%20there%20operationally%2C%26quot%3B%20Weiner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDomino's%20and%20Wingstop%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20across%20many%20industries%20are%20worried%20that%20their%20bosses%20will%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-ai-job-cuts-layoffs-corporate-speak-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20replace%20them%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Clifford%20said%20that%20Rime's%20restaurant%20