mates%20from%20my%20first%20year%20at%20EY%2C%20and%20my%20colleagues%20from%20over%2012%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanalyst-laid-off-deloitte-happier-work-culture-felt-toxic-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eburnout%20is%20real%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20long%20hours%2C%20tight%20deadlines%2C%20and%20constant%20pressure%20to%20perform%20can%20drain%20you%20if%20you%20don't%20set%20firm%20boundaries%20to%20protect%20your%20mental%2C%20physical%2C%20and%20spiritual%20well-being.%20And%20like%20any%20large%20organization%2C%20the%20politics%20and%20bureaucracy%20can%20be%20draining.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it's%20an%20accounting%20firm%20run%20by%20accountants.%20Metrics%20often%20win%20out%20over%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20after%2013%20years%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20quit%20and%20launch%20my%20own%20business%20after%20I%20realized%20staying%20would%20only%20be%20about%20the%20money%20and%20title.%20My%20faith%20played%20a%20significant%20role%2C%20showing%20me%20EY%20wasn't%20where%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20be.%20Working%20on%20the%20EY's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fmeet-the-finalists-for-the-ey-entrepreneur-of-the-year-australia-awards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEntrepreneur%20Of%20The%20Year%3C%2Fa%3E%20Award%20%E2%80%94%20a%20global%20program%20that%20recognizes%20outstanding%20entrepreneurs%20%E2%80%94%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20how%20much%20I%20admired%20people%20who%20took%20leaps%20of%20faith%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20my%20experience%20at%20EY%20became%20rocket%20fuel.%20It%20gave%20me%20the%20grit%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20the%20playbook%20to%20succeed%20in%20any%20professional%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20selling%20my%20fintech%20startup%20Ardius%20to%20Gusto%20in%202021%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsabbatical-burn