%20planned%20for%E2%80%94one%20that%20led%20to%20the%20founding%20of%20%3Cstrong%3EBharatRohan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20pioneering%20agri-tech%20company%20that%20now%20uses%20drone-based%20hyperspectral%20imaging%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F400346%2Fdeep-griha-academy-soil-testing-initiative-soil-testing-kits-sustainable-agriculture-real-world-projects%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonitor%20crop%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20support%20over%2050%2C000%20farmers%20across%20seven%20states%2C%20and%20reduce%20pesticide%20usage%20and%20input%20costs.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20college%20hobby%20evolved%20into%20a%20movement%20to%20make%20farming%20more%20precise%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20profitable%E2%80%94one%20flight%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECurious%20glances%20and%20crop%20questions%3A%20An%20accidental%20beginning%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20would%20gather%20around%20and%20ask%20us%20about%20their%20crops%2C%20including%20questions%20about%20pest%20attacks%2C%20yellowing%20leaves%2C%20diseases%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amandeep%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20assumed%20we%20knew%20the%20answers%20because%20we%20were%20engineering%20students.%20Even%20though%20we%20did%20not%20know%20the%20answers%20back%20in%202015%2C%20we%20were%20curious%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20began%20their%20journey%20by%20visiting%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendras%20(KVKs)%20to%20better%20understand%20agricultural%20issues.%20While%20these%20centres%20offered%20scientific%20support%2C%20they%20we