vember%2C%20when%20it%20restarts%2C%20volunteers%20return%20on%20their%20own%2C%20led%20by%20excitement%20and%20their%20shared%20sense%20of%20purpose.%20%E2%80%9CSaji%E2%80%99s%20pure%20passion%20towards%20the%20cause%2C%20his%20discipline%20in%20implementing%20it%20and%20his%20positive%20character%20keep%20me%20and%20many%20others%20inspired%20to%20keep%20coming%20back%20here.%20He%20has%20never%20accepted%20any%20monetary%20benefit%2C%20even%20if%20it%20was%20offered%20and%20that%20makes%20me%20want%20to%20show%20up%20for%20him%20and%20his%20cause%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Denny.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20quiet%20hum%20of%20excitement%20at%205%3A30%20AM%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20many%20lives%20Saji%20has%20touched%2C%20one%20story%20stands%20out.%20Aasim%20Velimanna%2C%20a%20differently-abled%20rights%20activist%20and%20motivational%20speaker%2C%20is%20now%20also%20a%20swimmer%20%E2%80%94%20thanks%20to%20Saji%E2%80%99s%20quiet%20persistence%20and%20belief%20in%20his%20potential.%20For%20two%20years%2C%20Saji%20gently%20built%20trust%20with%20Aasim%E2%80%99s%20parents%2C%20reassuring%20them%20that%20their%20son%20could%20safely%20learn%20to%20swim.%20When%20they%20finally%20agreed%2C%20he%20trained%20Aasim%20not%20just%20to%20float%20or%20paddle%2C%20but%20to%20cross%20the%20river.%20It%20was%20a%20powerful%20moment%2C%20not%20just%20for%20Aasim%20but%20for%20everyone%20who%20watched%20him%20break%20through%20perceived%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20river%20has%20seen%20many%20such%20milestones.%20One%20of%20Saji%E2%80%99s%20young%20students%20even%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Asian%20Book%20of%20Records%20for%20completing%20the%20longest%20solo%20open%20sea%20swim%20by%20a%20child%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feat%20born%20not%20of%20ambition%20alone%2C%20but%20of%20the%20joyful%2C%20disciplined%20training%20nurtured%20here%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%205%3A30%20AM%20every%20morning%2C%20a%20quiet%20hum%20of%20excitem