%20possible%2C%20says%20Dr%20Harish.%20(Representational%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Harish%20Chandra%20Reddy%2C%20Consultant%20Psychiatrist%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsually%20postpartum%20blues%20are%20something%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20mothers%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20they%20feel%20anxious%2C%20have%20mood%20swings%20and%20sleep%20disturbances.%20This%20generally%20resolves%20with%20some%20support%20from%20family%20and%20adequate%20rest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20husband%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20during%20this%20period.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20challenging%20role%20to%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20mood%20swings%20and%20symptoms%2C%20along%20with%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20child%20and%20other%20commitments.%20The%20way%20a%20husband%20manages%20the%20situation%2C%20his%20presence%2C%20his%20affection%20%E2%80%94%20all%20such%20gestures%20can%20be%20of%20great%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20to%20seek%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20emotional%20challenges%20of%20the%20postpartum%20period%20last%20beyond%20two%20weeks%2C%20it%20may%20point%20to%20Postpartum%20Depression%20(PPD)%2C%20which%20can%20bring%20intense%20mood%20changes%2C%20frequent%20crying%2C%20or%20feelings%20of%20being%20overwhelmed.%20In%20rare%20cases%2C%20some%20mothers%20may%20experience%20more%20severe%20symptoms%2C%20known%20as%20Postpartum%20Psychosis%2C%20which%20can%20include%20confusion%2C%20unusual%20thoughts%2C%20or%20strong%20emotional%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20conditions%20are%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331532%2Ftherapy-in-chennai-mental-health-cafe-wellness-centre-pooja-srinivasa-love-hope-company%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20treatable%20with%20the%20right%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Harish.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20support%20from%20loved%20ones%2C%20regular%20follow-ups%2C%20and%20professional%20guidance%20%E2%80%94%20often%20a%20mix%20of%20counselling%20and%20medication%20%E2%80%94%20recovery%20is%20very%20much%20possible.%20In%20most%20cases%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%2C%20mothers%20began%20to%20feel%20better%20within%20two%20to%20three%20weeks.%20Even%20when%20hospitalisation%20was%20needed%2C%20one%20mother%20recovered%20steadily%20within%2010%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20right%20care%2C%20postpartum%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20be%20a%20story%20of%20struggle.%20As%20Sharanya%20and%20Aminta%20show%2C%20it%20can%20also%20be%20a%20journey%20of%20healing%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20rediscovery%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20women%20are%20not%20left%20to%20do%20it%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748441400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D440326%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Between%20C-sections%2C%20breastfeeding%20challenges%2C%20and%20emotional%20trauma%2C%20these%20women%20found%20strength%20in%20their%20support%20systems%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20husband%20who%20asked%20the%20right%20questions%20to%20in-laws%20who%20quit%20their%20jobs%20to%20help.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F440326%2Fpostpartum-support-india-mothers-day-stories%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Simple%20At-Home%20Rainwater%20Harvesting%20Guide%20Can%20Help%20You%20Save%20Thousands%20of%20Litres%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20the%20monsoon%20brings%20chaos%20to%20Indian%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20flooded%20streets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20overflowing%20drains%20in%20Delhi%2C%20